                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              7. You generated the expected value of $S$, the outcomes of 1,000 bets that the ball lands in the green pocket, in the previous exercise.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
